at the court assembly

314
00:18:07,790 --> 00:18:09,070
and recorded,

315
00:18:09,070 --> 00:18:10,590
there's no taking it back.

316
00:18:10,790 --> 00:18:11,680
No worries, Ms. Amita.

317
00:18:12,200 --> 00:18:13,310
Heaven is my witness.

318
00:18:13,510 --> 00:18:15,550
I would never go back on my word.

319
00:18:17,590 --> 00:18:20,110
