320
00:18:20,350 --> 00:18:23,000
I ramble, so if you can't keep up,

321
00:18:23,200 --> 00:18:25,310
mark it with a circle first.

322
00:18:26,310 --> 00:18:27,150
Mr. Su,

323
00:18:27,830 --> 00:18:29,844
why are you helping the Litchi Envoy?

324
00:18:30,440 --> 00:18:33,640
