326
00:18:35,480 --> 00:18:36,350
I want to help

327
00:18:36,830 --> 00:18:39,110
everyone here as well.

328
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:43,080
Mr. Ma,

329
00:18:43,640 --> 00:18:45,070
if fresh litchis

330
00:18:45,200 --> 00:18:46,422
are delivered to Chang'an,

331
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:48,960
and Noble Consort
gets to taste them,

332
00:18:49,310 --> 00:18:50,200
what will she say?

333
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:51,920
If Her Highness tastes

334
00:18:51,920 --> 00:18:53,790
fresh litchis, she'll say,

335
00:18:54,880 --> 00:18:55,720
"Delicious.

336
00:18:56,440 --> 00:18:57,350
I want more.

337
00:18:57,790 --> 00:18:58,790
Are there more?"

338
00:19:01,480 --> 00:19:03,350
Yes, there are!

339
00:19:03,480 --> 00:19:04,830
If Noble Consort wants more,

340
00:19:04,830 --> 00:19:07,488
shouldn't we deliver more?

341
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:09,888
We'll have to deliver it every year.

342
00:19:09,911 --> 00:19:11,270
That means litchis from Gaozhou

343
00:19:11,550 --> 00:19:13,000
will become a regular tribute.

344
00:19:13,310 --> 00:19:14,480
An annual delivery.

345
00:19:15,066 --> 00:19:16,190
Everyone, think about it.

346
00:19:16,400 --> 00:19:17,955
What kind of business would that be?

347
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:20,880
Everlasting.

348
00:19:21,400 --> 00:19:22,830
Once-in-a-lifetime.

349
00:19:25,400 --> 00:19:27,400
