354
00:19:39,400 --> 00:19:41,830
If the Hu merchants fund it,

355
00:19:42,070 --> 00:19:45,510
the litchi delivery trial may succeed.

356
00:19:45,720 --> 00:19:47,160
Then if His Majesty asks about it,

357
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:52,311
and Litchi Envoy puts in
a few good words for us,

358
00:19:52,333 --> 00:19:53,830
would any of you still worry

359
00:19:54,310 --> 00:19:55,550
about losing out

360
00:19:56,070 --> 00:19:57,590
on this opportunity?

361
00:19:59,270 --> 00:20:00,110
When the time comes,

362
00:20:00,270 --> 00:20:02,110
litchi procurement and horse supply

363
00:20:02,400 --> 00:20:04,550
will all be in our control.

364
00:20:05,510 --> 00:20:07,350
Maybe post stations along the route

365
00:20:07,350 --> 00:20:09,480
would also be entrusted to us.

366
00:20:09,960 --> 00:20:11,240
It's a gold mine.

367
00:20:12,590 --> 00:20:14,000
Where else could you find

368
00:20:14,000 --> 00:20:15,333
a deal this good?

369
00:20:17,350 --> 00:20:19,160
I agree with Mr. Su.

370
00:20:20,240 --> 00:20:22,270
This is indeed a promising deal.

371
00:20:22,270 --> 00:20:23,790
Great minds think alike.

372
00:20:24,640 --> 00:20:25,920
