425
00:22:33,880 --> 00:22:35,310
The trial at the East Gate

426
00:22:35,510 --> 00:22:37,070
is meant to shorten the transport time

427
00:22:37,310 --> 00:22:39,240
as much as possible.

428
00:22:39,790 --> 00:22:41,030
Once it succeeds,

429
00:22:41,310 --> 00:22:44,030
fresh litchi delivery to Chang'an

430
00:22:44,160 --> 00:22:46,911
won't be impossible anymore.

431
00:22:56,110 --> 00:22:57,400
What do you say, guys?

432
00:23:05,510 --> 00:23:06,480
