439
00:23:23,110 --> 00:23:24,480
your loyalty to the imperial court

440
00:23:24,480 --> 00:23:26,866
won't be let down.

441
00:23:30,613 --> 00:23:31,640
Ms. Amita has a point.

442
00:23:32,510 --> 00:23:34,510
After all, you're putting in real money.

443
00:23:35,270 --> 00:23:38,000
It's good to be cautious.

444
00:23:38,888 --> 00:23:40,480
Since we're holding this court assembly

445
00:23:41,030 --> 00:23:42,000
to make money

446
00:23:42,000 --> 00:23:43,640
and seek good ventures,

447
00:23:44,070 --> 00:23:45,240
what harm is there

448
00:23:45,590 --> 00:23:46,888
in waiting a few days?

449
00:23:47,750 --> 00:23:50,400
As the saying goes,
"Patience is a dish best-served cold.

450
00:23:50,880 --> 00:23:53,311
A good match is worth waiting for."

451
00:24:02,200 --> 00:24:03,070
In that case,

452
00:24:03,790 --> 00:24:05,110
let's vote with ox bones

453
00:24:05,511 --> 00:24:07,911
