458
00:24:14,590 --> 00:24:16,240
Clap if you agree. Agree.

459
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:18,840
Very much agree.

460
00:24:19,720 --> 00:24:20,560
Agree.

461
00:24:41,070 --> 00:24:42,480
