00:31:14,790 --> 00:31:16,466
Please don't say that, Inspector He.

578
00:31:17,240 --> 00:31:19,070
Helping Gaozhou's tax revenues

579
00:31:19,480 --> 00:31:21,240
is our responsibility.

580
00:31:21,750 --> 00:31:23,480
For the development of Gaozhou,

581
00:31:23,480 --> 00:31:25,310
it's worth the effort.

582
00:31:25,880 --> 00:31:26,750
Well said.

583
00:31:28,510 --> 00:31:29,960
Today is a family banquet.

584
00:31:30,550 --> 00:31:32,400
Well,

585
00:31:32,400 --> 00:31:34,440
I invited you all

586
00:31:34,440 --> 00:31:35,680
as the godfather of Amita.

587
00:31:36,720 --> 00:31:38,200
The Hu Merchants' Association

588
00:31:38,510 --> 00:31:40,480
flourished

589
00:31:41,200 --> 00:31:42,777
thanks to your support.

590
00:31:44,550 --> 00:31:47,440
Amita is very young.

591
00:31:48,070 --> 00:31:49,480
Without your tolerance

592
00:31:49,960 --> 00:31:51,960
and help,

593
00:31:52,310 --> 00:31:53,590
she could never have succeeded.

594
00:31:54,711 --> 00:31:55,840
I offer this second toast

595
00:31:56,240 --> 00:31:58,030
as her godfather. I thank you all.

596
00:31:58,733 --> 00:31:59,688
We've not done enough.

597
00:31:59,711 --> 00:32:01,070
Inspector He, you're too kind.

598
00:32:01,070 --> 00:32:01,910
Cheers.

599
00:32:08,440 --> 00:32:10,240
Recently, I heard

600
00:32:10,960 --> 00:32:12,720
the court assembly

601
00:32:12,720 --> 00:32:15,270
was abruptly suspended.

602
00:32:15,830 --> 00:32:17,270
It seems like Su Liang

603
00:32:17,270 --> 00:32:18,510
made a proposal.

604
00:32:18,880 --> 00:32:19,720
Is that true?

605
00:32:33,310 --> 00:32:34,150
His Majesty

606
00:32:34,640 --> 00:32:36,400
likes our litchis,

607
00:32:37,270 --> 00:32:38,110
that's a good thing.

608
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:41,350
This is both a blessing
and an opportunity

609
00:32:42,240 --> 00:32:43,720
for people in Gaozhou.

610
00:32:44,288 --> 00:32:45,240
Am I right, Zhao?

611
00:32:45,960 --> 00:32:46,800
Exactly.

612
00:32:47,200 --> 00:32:47,880
In fact,

613
00:32:47,880 --> 00:32:51,240
Inspector He has always held
high hopes for this.

614
00:32:52,110 --> 00:32:53,270
Since the Litchi Envoy

615
00:32:53,270 --> 00:32:54,310
arrived in Gaozhou,

616
00:32:54,310 --> 00:32:56,044
he has been granted every convenience.

617
00:32:56,688 --> 00:32:57,920
But unexpectedly, this fellow

618
00:32:58,310 --> 00:32:59,880
is two-faced and insincere.

619
00:33:00,270 --> 00:33:01,310
Since arriving,

620
00:33:02,680 --> 00:33:03,510
he's used his title

621
00:33:03,510 --> 00:33:06,400
to swindle money.

622
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:08,640
But why did he rally the people

623
00:33:08,640 --> 00:33:10,880
and stage this delivery trial here?

624
00:33:11,400 --> 00:33:12,640
If he didn't run this trial,

625
00:33:12,866 --> 00:33:14,622
would you have the confidence
to fund him?

626
00:33:16,640 --> 00:33:18,510
This isn't a trial. It's a performance.

627
00:33:19,550 --> 00:33:20,480
(He's pretending)

628
00:33:20,720 --> 00:33:22,000
(as if he's dedicated,)

629
00:33:22,510 --> 00:33:24,110
(just to put on a show for you.)

630
00:33:32,590 --> 00:33:35,110
The horses are back!

631
00:33:38,400 --> 00:33:40,110
(When Li Shande)

632
00:33:40,355 --> 00:33:42,066
(requested to use the Little East Gate)

633
00:33:42,066 --> 00:33:43,160
(for his trial,)

634
00:33:43,400 --> 00:33:44,310
(I warned him)

635
00:33:44,680 --> 00:33:46,350
(the trial)

636
00:33:46,920 --> 00:33:48,270
(wouldn't lead him anywhere.)

637
00:33:48,550 --> 00:33:49,750
(How could it compare to)

638
00:33:49,750 --> 00:33:51,155
(delivery all the way to Chang'an?)

639
00:33:51,510 --> 00:33:52,480
(It's like blindfolding)

640
00:33:52,920 --> 00:33:56,110
(a donkey and making it
walk around the millstone)

641
00:33:56,110 --> 00:33:57,030
(a thousand times...)

642
00:33:57,288 --> 00:33:59,110
It'll never become
a thousand-mile-steed!

643
00:33:59,510 --> 00:34:01,560
Carry him to the well
to get some cold water.

644
00:34:01,830 --> 00:34:03,333
Add mint leaves.

645
00:34:03,333 --> 00:34:04,560
All right. I'll do it.

646
00:34:04,830 --> 00:34:05,680
Next rider.

647
00:34:05,680 --> 00:34:06,520
Who's the next rider?

648
00:34:06,750 --> 00:34:07,350
It's me.

649
00:34:07,350 --> 00:34:08,488
Hurry up and mount now.

650
00:34:09,044 --> 00:34:11,022
- Mint leaves! Hurry up!
- Be careful.

651
00:34:12,880 --> 00:34:14,840
(Shen Hour, You Hour)
(This is a childish trial.)

652
00:34:15,150 --> 00:34:16,510
Even if it succeeds,

653
00:34:17,150 --> 00:34:18,510
what does it prove?

654
00:34:20,150 --> 00:34:21,320
But this time, it's different.

655
00:34:21,670 --> 00:34:23,000
He's reaching into

656
00:34:23,022 --> 00:34:24,280
the Hu Merchants' Association,

657
00:34:26,670 --> 00:34:28,480
trying to move against the members

658
00:34:28,880 --> 00:34:30,000
and my family.

659
00:34:30,400 --> 00:34:32,400
I won't tolerate that.

660
00:34:33,280 --> 00:34:35,670
Now I'm truly upset.

661
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:37,400
Even if we take a generous view,

662
00:34:38,030 --> 00:34:39,960
let's say the trial works out,

663
00:34:40,150 --> 00:34:41,030
so what?

664
00:34:41,800 --> 00:34:43,911
Once he reaches Chang'an
and meets His Majesty,

665
00:34:43,911 --> 00:34:46,230
will he really mention all your names

666
00:34:47,070 --> 00:34:48,755
and give away the credit?

667
00:34:49,760 --> 00:34:51,110
The like of him, you know what,

668
00:34:51,840 --> 00:34:52,920
once they rise to the top,

669
00:34:53,155 --> 00:34:54,710
they definitely will turn against you.

670
00:34:56,150 --> 00:34:57,360
And when that happens,

671
00:34:57,840 --> 00:34:59,760
you'll lose everything.

672
00:35:02,000 --> 00:35:02,840
That's right.

673
00:35:03,320 --> 00:35:04,160
Usually,

674
00:35:05,190 --> 00:35:07,840
if your business fails,

675
00:35:08,320 --> 00:35:10,280
at least the goods are in your hands.

676
00:35:10,510 --> 00:35:11,760
You won't lose it all.

677
00:35:12,590 --> 00:35:14,110
But the litchi delivery

678
00:35:15,190 --> 00:35:17,360
is totally an impracticable project.

679
00:35:17,510 --> 00:35:18,480
If it goes south,

680
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:21,760
you'll lose everything.

681
00:35:22,320 --> 00:35:24,840
There'll be no turning back at all.

682
00:35:24,840 --> 00:35:26,760
Zhao, don't scare them.

683
00:35:27,710 --> 00:35:31,320
None of you have joined in yet, right?

684
00:35:32,320 --> 00:35:34,550
Actually, it's simple.

685
00:35:35,480 --> 00:35:36,320
When businessmen

686
00:35:37,360 --> 00:35:38,670
see an opportunity,

687
00:35:38,670 --> 00:35:40,710
they become thrilled.

688
00:35:41,360 --> 00:35:43,320
I've come up with a plan for you.

689
00:35:44,510 --> 00:35:46,440
We'll expand the route

690
00:35:46,670 --> 00:35:47,840
to Tazi next year.

691
00:35:48,550 --> 00:35:50,590
I promise your profit

692
00:35:51,000 --> 00:35:52,320
will increase by thirty percent.

693
00:35:52,800 --> 00:35:54,444
It's thirty percent after tax.

694
00:35:55,880 --> 00:35:56,880
That's lucrative.

695
00:36:01,150 --> 00:36:03,070
Do you mean it, Inspector He?

696
00:36:03,660 --> 00:36:05,800
Inspector He made this promise
right in front of you,

697
00:36:05,800 --> 00:36:06,620
how could it be false?

698
00:36:08,960 --> 00:36:10,960
Gaozhou is thriving today,

699
00:36:11,630 --> 00:36:13,133
thanks to your support.

700
00:36:13,333 --> 00:36:15,333
It's not easy to meet each other
across the sea.

701
00:36:15,400 --> 00:36:16,710
Inspector He held this banquet

702
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:17,960
to give everyone

703
00:36:18,230 --> 00:36:19,230
this opportunity.

704
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:20,510
We can collaborate

705
00:36:20,622 --> 00:36:21,760
and brave obstacles as one.

706
00:36:23,190 --> 00:36:24,360
That's enough.

707
00:36:25,110 --> 00:36:26,666
Stop giving a lofty speech.

708
00:36:27,880 --> 00:36:28,840
It's simple.

709
00:36:29,360 --> 00:36:31,480
When there's an opportunity,
we seize it together.

710
00:36:32,030 --> 00:36:34,030
When there's profit,
we earn it together.

711
00:36:34,880 --> 00:36:37,030
Anyway, as long as you're happy,

712
00:36:37,480 --> 00:36:38,590
I'm happy too.

713
00:36:40,000 --> 00:36:41,190
Inspector He, thank you

714
00:36:41,190 --> 00:36:42,550
for looking out for us.

715
00:36:43,110 --> 00:36:44,511
On behalf of the Hu merchants...

716
00:36:49,550 --> 00:36:51,510
I... I invite our elder,

717
00:36:52,377 --> 00:36:53,800
Mr. Gu, to offer a toast.

718
00:36:57,320 --> 00:36:58,160
Mr. Gu.

719
00:37:06,840 --> 00:37:09,360
Inspector He, you've devoted yourself to

720
00:37:09,360 --> 00:37:10,880
steering our course.

721
00:37:11,800 --> 00:37:12,960
I believe the Hu merchants

722
00:37:12,960 --> 00:37:14,177
will stay on the right path.

723
00:37:14,960 --> 00:37:17,110
Come, let's raise our cups
to Inspector He

724
00:37:17,440 --> 00:37:18,800
for leading us through the storm

725
00:37:18,800 --> 00:37:20,210
and bringing us a bountiful harvest.

726
00:37:20,280 --> 00:37:21,120
Well said!

727
00:37:22,030 --> 00:37:22,870
Cheers.

728
00:37:23,110 --> 00:37:24,190
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

729
00:37:24,960 --> 00:37:25,800
Be careful.

730
00:37:27,070 --> 00:37:27,910
Bring more water.

731
00:37:34,550 --> 00:37:36,400
Mr. Li.

732
00:37:37,800 --> 00:37:39,400
One of the litchis has split.

733
00:37:46,670 --> 00:37:47,550
This one was crushed.

734
00:37:47,710 --> 00:37:48,840
It's not spoiled.

735
00:37:48,840 --> 00:37:50,360
They're transported by horses.

736
00:37:50,590 --> 00:37:51,760
Damage is unavoidable.

737
00:37:53,044 --> 00:37:54,280
Wrap them in something soft.

738
00:37:55,280 --> 00:37:55,920
Wrap them up.

739
00:37:55,920 --> 00:37:57,670
Get cloth. Cloth.

740
00:37:57,670 --> 00:37:58,590
No, not cloth.

741
00:37:58,590 --> 00:38:00,440
It doesn't breathe. Use paper.

742
00:38:00,466 --> 00:38:01,470
There's paper over there.

743
00:38:01,880 --> 00:38:02,440
Here.

744
00:38:02,440 --> 00:38:03,280
Come on.

745
00:38:08,190 --> 00:38:09,155
How is he?

746
00:38:09,288 --> 00:38:10,320
He's feeling better now.

747
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:12,800
What a relief.

748
00:38:19,880 --> 00:38:20,720
Mr. Li,

749
00:38:22,000 --> 00:38:22,920
the heat is blazing.

750
00:38:24,190 --> 00:38:25,360
None of us can stand it.

751
00:38:27,000 --> 00:38:28,355
Luckily, he collapsed here.

752
00:38:29,190 --> 00:38:30,670
If it happened on the mountain road,

753
00:38:30,670 --> 00:38:31,960
he could've fallen off the horse.

754
00:38:31,960 --> 00:38:33,066
And if the horse ran off,

755
00:38:33,066 --> 00:38:34,488
how would we continue this trial?

756
00:38:35,840 --> 00:38:36,680
Mr. Li,

757
00:38:37,440 --> 00:38:39,088
we can tough it out.

758
00:38:41,190 --> 00:38:43,577
You're pushing yourselves too hard!

759
00:38:47,590 --> 00:38:49,230
Even if you can hold out,

760
00:38:49,311 --> 00:38:50,240
what about the horses?

761
00:38:50,920 --> 00:38:52,070
They can't.

762
00:38:53,150 --> 00:38:54,630
Those two strong horses

763
00:38:55,150 --> 00:38:56,760
may handle another half-day journey,

764
00:38:57,360 --> 00:38:58,630
but they can't last for more.

765
00:38:58,733 --> 00:39:00,311
Then, let's finish the half-day journey.

766
00:39:00,590 --> 00:39:01,670
What difference

767
00:39:01,670 --> 00:39:02,590
will it make?

768
00:39:03,030 --> 00:39:04,510
If shouting louder wins the argument,

769
00:39:04,840 --> 00:39:06,488
we might as well listen to donkeys.

770
00:39:07,030 --> 00:39:07,880
Why are you shouting?

771
00:39:08,844 --> 00:39:11,044
We listen to Mr. Li
when it comes to the trial.

772
00:39:16,110 --> 00:39:16,950
Well.

773
00:39:17,590 --> 00:39:18,430
Mr. Lan,

774
00:39:19,510 --> 00:39:21,110
I don't know you before,

775
00:39:21,500 --> 00:39:23,360
but since everyone
respectfully calls you Mr. Lan,

776
00:39:23,360 --> 00:39:24,200
I'll do the same.

777
00:39:25,030 --> 00:39:25,710
This trial

778
00:39:25,710 --> 00:39:27,377
isn't just theory on paper.

779
00:39:27,960 --> 00:39:29,230
The road to Chang'an is 2500 km,

780
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:30,960
and is full of obstacles

781
00:39:31,710 --> 00:39:34,030
that you can't foresee.

782
00:39:34,466 --> 00:39:35,550
The purpose of the trial

783
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:37,000
is to discover problems

784
00:39:37,000 --> 00:39:37,840
and avoid them.

785
00:39:38,320 --> 00:39:40,800
If we were only testing for speed,

786
00:39:40,800 --> 00:39:41,590
that'd be easy.

787
00:39:41,590 --> 00:39:43,710
We could take the average
from the first three days

788
00:39:43,710 --> 00:39:44,550
and calculate it.

789
00:39:44,710 --> 00:39:45,888
But that's not the point.

790
00:39:46,320 --> 00:39:47,150
Only when a trial

791
00:39:47,150 --> 00:39:48,840
goes on long enough,

792
00:39:49,030 --> 00:39:50,630
people fall, and jars break,

793
00:39:50,960 --> 00:39:52,280
we include all kinds of problems

794
00:39:52,510 --> 00:39:54,320
to get the results

795
00:39:54,670 --> 00:39:55,630
that are meaningful.

796
00:40:00,440 --> 00:40:01,280
Mr. Li...

797
00:40:02,200 --> 00:40:04,155
As long as there's still one horse left,

798
00:40:04,550 --> 00:40:05,390
I'll keep going.

799
00:40:06,280 --> 00:40:07,190
We will too.

800
00:40:07,760 --> 00:40:08,600
Same here.

801
00:40:10,960 --> 00:40:11,960
I appreciate that.

802
00:40:15,670 --> 00:40:18,630
It's not that I want to give up.

803
00:40:20,480 --> 00:40:21,510
My two friends

804
00:40:22,510 --> 00:40:24,550
have never ridden like this
without rest.

805
00:40:25,800 --> 00:40:26,760
Let them withdraw.

806
00:40:28,400 --> 00:40:29,240
I'll stay.

807
00:40:34,630 --> 00:40:35,470
Thank you.

808
00:40:38,880 --> 00:40:39,720
Now,

809
00:40:40,355 --> 00:40:41,550
we're short on riders.

810
00:40:43,150 --> 00:40:44,880
Let's adjust the plan. Riders and horses

811
00:40:44,911 --> 00:40:46,377
swap out every three rounds.

812
00:40:46,488 --> 00:40:48,444
At least everyone
gets a full night's rest.

813
00:40:48,888 --> 00:40:50,244
What do you all think?

814
00:40:51,510 --> 00:40:52,350
Good.

815
00:40:53,030 --> 00:40:53,870
Good.

816
00:41:12,150 --> 00:41:12,990
Jar C.

817
00:41:12,990 --> 00:41:15,300
(The Fifth Day of the Trial)

818
00:41:18,190 --> 00:41:19,030
Jar C.

819
00:41:20,360 --> 00:41:22,000
What's the condition in Jar C?

820
00:41:23,230 --> 00:41:24,110
Mr. Li,

821
00:41:24,320 --> 00:41:26,230
litchis in Jar C have no problem.

822
00:41:26,360 --> 00:41:28,190
- Good.
- Well done.

823
00:41:29,710 --> 00:41:30,550
Chief Scribe Zhao,

824
00:41:31,630 --> 00:41:32,800
how's the trial going?

825
00:41:32,822 --> 00:41:34,320
Riders and horses are exhausted.

826
00:41:34,510 --> 00:41:35,440
Some have withdrawn.

827
00:41:35,840 --> 00:41:37,070
Only a few riders left.

828
00:41:37,311 --> 00:41:38,320
They're barely holding on.

829
00:41:39,200 --> 00:41:40,844
What about the man I told you to watch?

830
00:41:40,955 --> 00:41:42,030
He's done the most laps.

831
00:41:43,030 --> 00:41:44,070
He's done the most laps.

832
00:41:45,777 --> 00:41:47,511
Then he must be close to collapse.

833
00:41:47,666 --> 00:41:48,920
If anything happens to him

834
00:41:48,920 --> 00:41:49,710
in the mountains,

835
00:41:49,710 --> 00:41:51,110
it wouldn't be surprising.

836
00:41:53,110 --> 00:41:53,950
Coming through.

837
00:41:54,510 --> 00:41:56,550
Make way.

838
00:41:56,590 --> 00:41:57,430
You guys...

839
00:41:57,630 --> 00:41:58,000
Mr. Li.

840
00:41:58,030 --> 00:41:58,870
Go to the back hill

841
00:41:59,280 --> 00:42:00,030
and lay the rope.

842
00:42:00,030 --> 00:42:01,044
Don't let me keep you.

843
00:42:01,060 --> 00:42:02,644
Target at Yan Yazhuang's horse.

844
00:42:07,000 --> 00:42:08,644
Quick. The horse is approaching.

845
00:42:18,590 --> 00:42:20,088
They're coming. Get ready.

846
00:42:31,980 --> 00:42:34,820
=The Litchi Road=

847
00:42:35,070 --> 00:42:36,280
His Majesty and Noble Consort

848
00:42:36,590 --> 00:42:38,510
may soon taste fresh litchis.

849
00:42:38,800 --> 00:42:40,711
It's as if the fruit
is already in their mouths.

850
00:42:41,030 --> 00:42:41,870
Impressive, Bro...

851
00:42:42,670 --> 00:42:43,880
You're outstanding.

852
00:42:45,920 --> 00:42:46,760
Li Shande,

853
00:42:47,880 --> 00:42:48,800
Jar B is leaking.

854
00:42:49,150 --> 00:42:49,990
Leaking?

855
00:42:51,800 --> 00:42:53,400
The trial fails?

856
00:42:53,444 --> 00:42:54,688
I want to live.

857
00:42:54,777 --> 00:42:55,666
Father!

858
00:42:58,360 --> 00:43:00,177
I'm desperate to live!

859
00:43:02,960 --> 00:43:04,000
I'll risk my life

860
00:43:04,150 --> 00:43:05,840
to make this deal work.

861
00:43:06,000 --> 00:43:07,400
I won't disappoint

862
00:43:07,440 --> 00:43:08,800
the support you gave me.

863
